snippet.textDisplay:
Saeyyoni was a flop

but this was magical

Why?

Music is a language...

The strange thing which only some would understand that Guitars and Drums were leading everything through out the song...

This is a folk song... Guitars and Drums are not supposed to be so noticable through out this extreme folk song but like i said.... Music is a language.

Its a strange,unusual composition but yet nostalgic... A modern instrument is leading all the way throughout the song waking folk instruments one by one blowing lives into them once again...

A Nostalgic memory... 

Beautiful ❤️

Akbar Ali ❤️
